                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d225">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">White</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-02-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 8, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At present, importation live plants absolutely prohibited. Fresh fruit, not
                    infected, admitted freely. Chancellor would probably not receive merchants.
                    Desired statements could be transmitted through embassy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">White.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
